<div class="com-share" data-id="21344" data-title="《阿迪达斯新广告，任性地不怎么用明星们的正脸》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/21344/medium/21344.JPG?1453820821" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/21344.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
